specified config file (defaults to $HOME/.eucarc or /etc/euca2ools/eucarc).
.PP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR                      Display this help message.
.PP
\fB\-\-version\fR                       Display the version of this tool.
.PP
\fB\-\-debug\fR                         Turn on debugging.
.PP
